fields.description:
Please refer to style guide for most of the notes below. 

See the attached screenshot of staging that references the numbered items:

1. Per style guide, white space below logo should be 22px, currently about 32 px in staging.

2. Adjust all space between menu buttons to match style guide; currently there is less space in staging than prescribed. Also chevron should be bottom-aligned with the text next to it.

5. Horizontal line should have 30 px buffering on each edge of it. (same with text below it)

6. Per style guide, there should be more white space below "Open all +"

7. Match "Medication Guide" language color to style guide (#414141)

8. Update line height to match style guide

9. Update font size and line height to match style guide.

10. Adjust the space before and after vertical line to better match comp; too much space in staging.
